See http://aqla.net

Contrubutions are welcome!

Build requirements:
Windows
Sandcastle
.NET 4

Put to /deployscript:
UnityEngine.dll
UnityEditor.dll
ILMerge.exe
zip.exe

You can get everything here
http://www.megafileupload.com/1B09/jl_deployscript_files.zip

Make build:
run /deployscript/!DeployFull.bat
open in unity "JustLogicBuildTest"
export asset


Merging all units to core JustLogic.dll library is required for backward compatibility.
